{"type": "article", "id": 21218, "title": "日落蜡烛", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-25T07:30:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160608133316af2jkQY4DhuvbGop.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是 nendo 推出的蜡烛，它在白色的外表下有一个奇妙的彩色分层。当蜡烛从上至下燃烧时，靠近灯芯处按顺序出现黄、橙、红、紫、蓝 5 种颜色，非常清新。蜡烛的设计取名“Sunset”，颜色的选择和变化源于日落时的天空，从白日到晚霞满天，在美好的遐想中暗示了时间的流逝。此外，不同的颜色对应了佛手柑、柠檬草、马郁兰、薰衣草和天竺葵的气味，这种气味的变化也能让人感受到变化的时间。<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/sunset-2/?erelease\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150830UspHEn2hmtR95Vak.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"579\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70782396\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150830nz4E7PwdTbpromvu.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150831VvMUC9haeimgLHyt.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150831bz6ZUiWrKSFJYpBI.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261508324HFhcvJX5rYSwPp2.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}